import { TextField } from "@mui/material"
import { Link } from "react-router-dom"

export const Login=()=>{

    const login=(e)=>{

    }

    return <>
        <form onSubmit={(e)=>login(e)}>
        <TextField id="tzInput" label="identity" variant="outlined" required />
        <TextField id="telInput" label="phone" variant="outlined" required />
        <TextField id="passwordInput" label="password" variant="outlined" required />
        <TextField id="submitInput" label="submit" variant="outlined" required />
            <Link>register</Link>
        </form>
    </>
}
